title: Who is Sylvette?
content: Palimo Prayoga, also known as Sylvette, Kurumi, Najenda, Arisu, and countless other aliases, is an FPS game GOAT from Tigaraksa, Tangerang, Indonesia. He is considered one of the best players in gaming history. He is the first player to achieve a 99,999 KD rating and a 100% headshot rate in high-rank lobbies across all the video games he plays. Don't believe me? Contact me, and I'll provide proof.
